      • Network

        public Network​(java.lang.String name,
               int nstations,
               int nslots,
               double side,
               float nbikes)
        throws java.lang.Exception
        Create a network with the specified number of stations uniformly distributed over a square with a randomly distributed bikes over all stations
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the network
        nstations - the count of stations to be created in the network
        nslots - the count of slots over each station
        side - the measure of side square
        nbikes - the initial population of bicycle percentage
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - In case the parameter nbikes isn't between 0 and 1
